      "value": "<p>@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.rules.JournalEntry.TZZMY71d2jc4MU6r.JournalEntryPage.IbFAlVfblDLuHwGo]{Skill Focus Feat}</p><hr /><p>You know how to make the airwaves—such as they are in space—work for you.</p>\n<p><strong>Prerequisites:</strong> Member of a charter that has completed the broadcast studio project.</p>\n<p><strong>Benefit:</strong> When in a settlement that contains a broadcast studio, you can use the airwaves to manage elements of your charter from afar, allowing you to handle @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.rules.JournalEntry.JrhxNmNVikgYLrhY.JournalEntryPage.SL59U85nyiXJ1iWm]{charter events} and perform @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.rules.JournalEntry.JrhxNmNVikgYLrhY.JournalEntryPage.0yOsYWEkn4y1pL7B]{downtime activities} related to charter management as though you were in any of your settlements. In addition, you gain a +2 insight bonus to a media-related Profession skill of your choice, such as vidgamer, comedian, or video personality.</p>"
